---
<BaseLayout>
  <article class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-3xl">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      Short bio. What you enjoy building, a sentence on your values, and what you’re exploring now.
    </p>

    <h2>Experience (brief)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Role @ Company</strong> — 2024–present · one-liner impact</li>
      <li><strong>Role @ Company</strong> — 2023–2024 · one-liner impact</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:you@example.com">Email</a> ·
      <a href="https://github.com/yourhandle">GitHub</a> ·
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yourhandle">LinkedIn</a>
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
